              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <br /><br>
          <p class ="after-word">Educational best practices and pedagogy remain a strong focus throughout the ACLTC Corporate Training program. Throughout all training modules, our educator-instructors implement a philosophy that includes Understanding by Design (UbD), Guided Practice, Peer Review, Analysis & Evaluation, Collaboration, and Group & Independent Work.</p><br />
